</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V2><H4>2</H4></TD><TD><P>Are there not mockers  
with me? and doth not mine eye continue in their provocation?</P></TD></TR><TR> 
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V3><H4>3</H4></TD><TD><P>Lay down now, put me in a       
surety with thee; who is he that will strike hands with me?</P></TD></TR><TR>   
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V4><H4>4</H4></TD><TD><P>For thou hast hid their heart   
from understanding: therefore shalt thou not exalt them.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD   
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V5><H4>5</H4></TD><TD><P>He that speaketh flattery to his    
friends, even the eyes of his children shall fail.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD         
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V6><H4>6</H4></TD><TD><P>He hath made me also a byword of    
the people; and aforetime I was as a tabret.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A 
NAME=V7><H4>7</H4></TD><TD><P>Mine eye also is dim by reason of sorrow, and all 
my members are as a shadow.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V8><H4>     
8</H4></TD><TD><P>Upright men shall be astonied at this, and the innocent shall 
stir up himself against the hypocrite.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A       
NAME=V9><H4>9</H4></TD><TD><P>The righteous also shall hold on his way, and he  
that hath clean hands shall be stronger and stronger.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD      
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V10><H4>10</H4></TD><TD><P>But as for you all, do ye return, 
and come now: for I cannot find one wise man among you.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD    
VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V11><H4>11</H4></TD><TD><P>My days are past, my purposes are 
broken off, even the thoughts of my heart.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A   
NAME=V12><H4>12</H4></TD><TD><P>They change the night into day: the light is    
short because of darkness.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V13><H4>     
13</H4></TD><TD><P>If I wait, the grave is mine house: I have made my bed in    
the darkness.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V14><H4>14</H4></TD><TD>  
<P>I have said to corruption, Thou art my father: to the worm, Thou art my      
mother, and my sister.</P></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V15><H4>15</H4>  
</TD><TD><P>And where is now my hope? as for my hope, who shall see it?</P></TD>
</TR><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP><A NAME=V16><H4>16</H4></TD><TD><P>They shall go down   
to the bars of the pit, when our rest together is in the dust.</P></TD></TR>    
